                                    <li>Create Tickets Entries</li>
                                    <li>View ticket Entries to projects they belong to</li>
                                    <li>View tickets they have created</li>
                                    <li>View Ticket Details to tickets they have created</li>
                                    <li>Edit Ticket Type, Title and Description to tickets they have created</li>
                                    <li>Edit Ticket Priority to tickets they have created</li>
